snippet: Kevin Na, whose laborious preshot routine became a major talking point during the Players Championship, was 10 strokes off the lead after shooting an opening-round 76 at the Memorial.
abstract: Scott Stallings takes first-round lead at Memorial golf tournament; Kevin Na, whose laborious preshot routine became a major talking point during the Players Championship, trails by 10 strokes.
lead_paragraph: Kevin Na, whose laborious preshot routine became a major talking point during the Players Championship, was 10 strokes off the lead after shooting an opening-round 76 at the Memorial.
